# Scripts

- All npm scripts delegate to `scripts/*.mjs` — keep package.json thin
- `dev.mjs` — electron-vite dev with main/preload/renderer
- `build.mjs` — production compile all processes
- `package.mjs` — electron-builder for installers

## Conventions

- Use `node:` imports and ESM in `.mjs` files
- Cross-platform paths via `path` module
- Do not embed secrets in scripts
- Exit non-zero on failure for CI

## Resources

- Icons and entitlements in `resources/` — referenced from builder config
